de.fha.dpmi.modeling.bpmn.elements

Interface Participant

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ParticipantImpl

    public interface Participant
    A participant of a collaboration is depicted as a pool, where a pool is used to divide FlowObjects from one another, it might contain one or more Lanes. This Interface is only used as a type definition and does only provide inherited methods.
